headline: Unstructured Data Pioneer Diskover Unveils $7.5M Seed Round, Investment by Snowflake Ventures, NetApp; and CloudSoda Acquisition
summary: RENO, Nev., June 17, 2025--Diskover is announcing three milestones: a $7.5M seed round, partnerships with NetApp and Snowflake; and the acquisition of CloudSoda.
